sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CreateGoalForm
    participant Validation
    participant Store
    participant APIService
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Navigate to Create Goal page
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Select goal type: Quantitative
    CreateGoalForm->>CreateGoalForm: Display quantitative-specific fields
    
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Enter: Title, Description, Category, Priority
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Enter: Start Value (200), Target Value (180), Current Value (200), Unit (pounds)
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Set: Allow Decimals (No)
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Optionally set: Start Date, Deadline
    
    User->>CreateGoalForm: Click "Create Goal"
    CreateGoalForm->>Validation: Validate all fields
    Validation-->>CreateGoalForm: Validation result
    
    alt Validation fails
        CreateGoalForm->>User: Display field-level errors
        User->>CreateGoalForm: Fix errors
        CreateGoalForm->>Validation: Re-validate
    end
    
    CreateGoalForm->>Store: Optimistic update: createGoalPending()
    Store->>Store: Add temporary goal with loading state
    
    CreateGoalForm->>APIService: createGoal(goalData)
    APIService->>APIService: Transform data to API format
    APIService->>APIService: Convert dates to ISO strings
    APIService->>APIService: Set defaults (progress: 0)
    APIService->>Backend: POST /api/goals
    
    Backend->>Validation: Server-side validation
    Validation-->>Backend: Validation result
    
    alt Validation fails
        Backend-->>APIService: 400 Bad Request with errors
        APIService->>Store: createGoalError(error)
        Store->>Store: Remove temporary goal, set error state
        CreateGoalForm->>User: Show error message
    else Validation succeeds
        Backend->>Backend: Check user permissions
        Backend->>Backend: Generate: id (UUID), createdAt, updatedAt
        Backend->>Database: INSERT goal record
        Database-->>Backend: Goal created
        Backend-->>APIService: 201 Created with goal data
        
        APIService->>APIService: Transform response (dates, etc.)
        APIService->>Store: createGoalSuccess(goal)
        Store->>Store: Remove temporary goal
        Store->>Store: Add real goal to store
        Store->>Store: Update goal list cache
        
        CreateGoalForm->>User: Show success message
        CreateGoalForm->>User: Navigate to goal detail page
        CreateGoalForm->>User: Clear form (if staying on page)
    end

